Title: smashr: Smoothing using Adaptive Shrinkage in R
Version: 1.1-0
Date: 2018-04-17
Description: Fast, wavelet-based Empirical Bayes shrinkage methods for
signal denoising, including smoothing Poisson-distributed data and
Gaussian-distributed data with possibly heteroskedastic error.
